title: 12 OCLOCK HIGH 105 Climate of Doubt [retr?tv]
description:
12 O&#039;CLOCK HIGH

104. Climate of Doubt  10/23/1964  (repost)
Crowe wants the 918th to bomb two targets on the next mission, first the Rouen marshaling yards, the second being a Gestapo building the French Resistance wants destroyed. The risks of flying two missions on one run is high and Savage is concerned that Crowes insistance on the second target may be being influenced by his feelings for the French resistance fighter Nicole Trouchard.
